<div id="disclaimer-modal" class="modal-overlay" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeModal()">
  <div class="modal-content">
    <h2>DISCLAIMER!</h2>
    <p>The tools in <b>XCellence</b> help organize and track academic tasks and grades but do not replace official records. Always refer to your teacher’s records for accuracy.</p>
    <button class="continue-btn" onclick="continueDashboard()">Continue</button>
